						<div class="postbody">How do you plan to handle IRQs triggered by the PPU? MMC3 and MMC5 watch PA12 or PA13 to count scanlines. If you're running the CPU ahead, you'll need to estimate how many scanlines ahead the IRQ is going to occur.</div>

