						<div class="postbody">Well I've been reading those links and yutzing around with optimizing and stabalizing the preemptive approach.  I have come to the agreement that lock-free techniques are not worth the trouble, at least not until std::atomic is widely implemented.
<br />
<br />Just about ready to start initial performance benchmarks before I do the "queue register writes" thing.</div>

